    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offering an E46 M3 powered by the iconic S54 3.2L inline-six, featuring individual throttle bodies and dual-VANOS for peak volumetric efficiency. This example features the desirable Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox and a factory limited-slip differential. Mechanically robust, it has undergone subframe reinforcement and a recent valve clearance adjustment to ensure optimal shim tolerances. The suspension geometry remains true, providing the communicative feedback and high-speed stability expected of this chassis. While showing honest cosmetic wear consistent with its age, the drivetrain is dialed in and the power delivery remains linear up to the 8,000 RPM redline.",
